WEBVTT

00:01.701 --> 00:04.536
        Cheers <i>is filmed</i>        
 <i>before a live studio audience.</i> 

00:04.571 --> 00:07.506
     I got something to add     
      to the conversation.      

00:07.540 --> 00:09.008
    If a 100-megaton warhead    

00:09.042 --> 00:10.509
    detonated over the city     
        of Boston,              

00:10.543 --> 00:11.844
the results                     

00:11.878 --> 00:12.978
            would be so horrific

00:13.013 --> 00:15.280
    that the survivors          
      would envy the dead.      

00:18.385 --> 00:21.153
    We weren't having           
     a conversation, Cliff.     

00:23.023 --> 00:25.557
  Well! Then food for thought.  

00:25.625 --> 00:27.092
      (theme song begins)       

00:31.297 --> 00:33.565
    ¶ Making your way           
      in the world today ¶      

00:33.600 --> 00:36.802
¶ Takes everything you've got ¶ 

00:36.836 --> 00:39.471
        ¶ Taking a break        
    from all your worries ¶     

00:39.506 --> 00:42.941
¶ Sure would help a lot ¶       

00:42.976 --> 00:46.812
      ¶ Wouldn't you like       
         to get away? ¶         

00:47.914 --> 00:50.849
  ¶ Sometimes you want to go ¶  

00:50.884 --> 00:54.853
    ¶ Where everybody           
    knows your name ¶           

00:56.156 --> 01:00.793
      ¶ And they're always      
        glad you came ¶         

01:00.827 --> 01:03.062
         ¶ You wanna be         
      where you can see ¶       

01:03.096 --> 01:05.631
         ¶ Our troubles         
    are all the same ¶          

01:05.665 --> 01:09.902
      ¶ You wanna be where      
  everybody knows your name ¶   

01:11.137 --> 01:13.872
         ¶ You wanna go         
      where people know ¶       

01:13.907 --> 01:16.342
  ¶ People are all the same ¶   

01:16.376 --> 01:20.846
      ¶ You wanna go where      
  everybody knows your name. ¶  

